### 1. Login User
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8082/v1/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "32323232",
    "pin": "3232"
}

### 2. Fetch Auctions (authentifié)
GET http://localhost:8082/v1/api/auctions
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 3. Créer une demande d'ajout d'auction
POST http://localhost:8082/v1/api/requests/auctions
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "iPhone 15 Pro Max",
    "description": "Smartphone Apple en excellent état",
    "starting_price": 15000,
    "category_id": 1,
    "location": "Casablanca"
}

### 4. Créer une demande d'ajout de banner annonce
POST http://localhost:8082/v1/api/requests/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Promo Ramadan 2025",
    "description": "Bannière publicitaire pour les offres spéciales",
    "image_url": "https://example.com/banner.jpg",
    "link_url": "https://mazadpay.com/offres"
}

